      "content": "i honestly dont even know why im typing this. it feels useless. i just spent the last three years of my life pouring everything into this research and now the lab is being defunded and my advisor won't even take my calls. it feels like my whole identity just evaporated overnight. i am just so tired. not like \"i need a nap\" tired, but like... i am exhausted at a level i didnt know was possible. i just want the noise to stop. i want everything to just be quiet and still.",
